   <item>
    <widget class="QLabel" name="instructionsLabel">
     <property name="text">
      <string>Instructions:
1. Load your volume (NIfTI format recommended)
2. Create two fiducial points as seed points
3. Set the radius estimate (approximate size of structure to segment)
4. Configure nnUNet settings (results path, model type, dataset)
5. Select or create output segmentation
6. Click "Run SeqSeg"

Note: 
- SeqSeg package will be installed automatically if needed
- nnUNet results path must point to trained models
- First run may take longer due to model setup</string>
     </property>
     <property name="wordWrap">
      <bool>true</bool>
